snippet.title: Lake of Voices Trailer
snippet.description:
Kickstarter: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/gbpatch/lake-of-voices-horror-visual-novel

Lake of Voices is a free dark fantasy, tragedy, horror Visual Novel being developed by GB Patch Games. It's a choice heavy game where death is simply inevitable. Not everyone is going to make it to the other side. It will be your actions that determine who does and who doesn't.

The game will be released for Windows, Mac, Linux, and Steam. An Android port is likely though would be released later than the other builds. 

Discord Community..........https://discord.gg/Q9YvQx2
Tumblr................................https://gb-patch.tumblr.com/
Twitter................................https://twitter.com/Patch_Games
Facebook...........................https://www.facebook.com/GBPatchGames/
